rder: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">0..*</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"StructureDefinition-Any.html\">Any</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">The EHR object is the root object and access point of an EHR for a subject of care.<br class=\"constraint\"/><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">Constraints: </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Contributions valid\" class=\"constraint\">Contributions_valid</span><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Ehr access valid\" class=\"constraint\">Ehr_access_valid</span><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Ehr status valid\" class=\"constraint\">Ehr_status_valid</span><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Compositions valid\" class=\"constraint\">Compositions_valid</span><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Directory valid must be present\" class=\"constraint\">Directory_valid</span><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Folders valid must be present\" class=\"constraint\">Folders_valid</span><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Directory in folders must be present\" class=\"constraint\">Directory_in_folders</span><br/></td></tr>#xD;\n<tr style=\"border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: #F7F7F7\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-